name: imperfect drawings #2
description:
Animated GIF | 6 fps| 2048 x 2048 | RGB | sRGB IEC61966-2.1


Walking towards the light is dazzling. What happens then when you touch it?

I love to see the waving forms that arise because of my inability to recreate the same line work, as a human being. So I created this animated GIF to share the beauty of human imperfection.


D.G.
